<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Aktivasi Pendaftaran</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 0;
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
    "
  >
    <table
      width="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      style="background-color: #f1f1f1"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table
            width="600"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="
              background-color: #ffffff;
              border: 1px solid #dddddd;
              border-radius: 15px;
              overflow: hidden;
            "
          >
            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://res.cloudinary.com/raafi/image/upload/v1745205582/bi-logo-text_junvjr.png"
                  alt="BI Logo"
                  width="250"
                  style="display: block"
                />
              </td>
            </tr>
            <!-- Content -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 20px">
                <p>Halo <strong><%= full_name %></strong> ðŸ‘‹</p>
                <p>
                  Terima kasih telah mendaftar Program Magang di Kantor
                  Perwakilan Bank Indonesia Provinsi Jawa Tengah. Berikut
                  informasi pendaftaran Anda:
                </p>

                <table cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Nama Lengkap</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= full_name %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Email</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= email %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>No Telp</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= phone %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Universitas</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= university %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Semester</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= semester %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>IPK</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= IPK %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Kategori Magang</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= intern_category %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Jurusan</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= college_major %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Bidang Kerja</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= division_request %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Link Berkas</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= google_drive_link %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Bulan Mulai</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= start_month %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Bulan Selesai</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= end_month %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Tanggal Pendaftaran</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= createdAt %></td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <p style="margin-top: 20px">
                  Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan, silakan hubungi kami.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-top: 40px">Hormat kami,</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 40px">
                  Humas Kantor Perwakilan Bank Indonesia Provinsi Jawa Tengah
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align="center"
                style="
                  background-color: #005596;
                  color: #ffffff;
                  padding: 20px;
                  font-size: 12px;
                "
              >
                &copy; 2025 Kantor Perwakilan Bank Indonesia Provinsi Jawa
                Tengah.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
